# Email Configuration for Newsletter Subscriptions
# Follow these steps to enable email notifications:

# STEP 1: Set up Gmail App Password
# 1. Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 2. Select "Mail" and "Windows Computer" (or your device)
# 3. Copy the generated 16-character password
# 4. Add it below

EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx

# NOTE: 
# - This uses Gmail SMTP. If using a different email service, update the transporter config in server.js
# - Keep these credentials secure and never commit to version control
# - Rename this file to .env and fill in your actual credentials to enable email sending
